phrases: You are actually a daughter of a really rich family.
And you ran away from home, right?
What is with you all of a sudden?
I bet you ate some super fancy food, did not you?
Man, you are makin' me hungry!
Like fish from around the world!
I knew that is where you were going.
If it is love and dreams and you it will become magical.
Now, let us cast a smile spell!
I kind of admired this powerful world,
Frozen time has started to move again
I do not need any complicated answers.
Simple feelings are the most important.
You can change those tears she would on sad nights into strength.
Now, let us cast a smile spell!
It is then that a single man arrives.
It is nice to have days like this once in a while.
It is kind of lonely, though.
I would have been able to dig it up...
You are still talking about that?
I could so care less about that already!
Let us go on a job!
What will I do about this month's rent?
Let us go on a job.
That is a quick about-face, Natsu.
You are finally in the mood to work again!
Well, I have always been working...
But lately I have been getting a feeling like I am being watched.
What do they call that again?
It is called being overly self-conscious!
I hope it is just my imagination!
Those two really do get along.
We will meet up at noon tomorrow,'kay?
Tomorrow's... going to be a fun... day of work!
I wonder what I should wear?
Be careful on your way home!
And... what is with those clothes?
My company, my house, my money...
All the private property was used as collateral, see...
Is this my reward for being a serious businessman all these years?!
That is where mom's grave is!
It is not so much sad, as it is laughable.
That much wealth, gone in an instant.
All my long years of achievement, to naught in a single night...
The money I worked so hard for I even sacrificed my family!
To see my daughter's face, Lucy.
And I told you not to lay a hand on Fairy Tail!
I do not have that kind of power now.
I only came to see how my daughter was doing.
Please, do not give me that kind of look.
I am sorry about everything that happened.
I do not plan to remain here long.
I am going to go work at a trade guild in Acalypha.
I am going to start all over again.
You will see it soon if you travel to the west from here.
I am going to need some money.
Would you lend it to me?
There is no way I have that!
I am sure you have that much on hand.
What the hell are you spouting?
And I am putting my pride aside to beg you for it!
I do not know what you are saying...
Is this how you treat your father?
I told you back then, remember?
What I want is not money, or pretty dresses, or fortune forced upon me...
And the same goes for you, Father.
You do not have any fortunes waiting for you!
How could he stoop so low?
Lucy, there is no one suspicious around here.
This private here lacks enthusiasm, sir!
Do not tell me he is...
I have spotted a questionable subject!
What are you doing, you jerk?
So it was Gray that was following Lucy!
I heard that Lucy was being followed by someone suspicious,
so I could not just leave her alone!
I came to see how she was doing.
What kind of running gag is that?!
but you just dropped even worse in my book, Gray!
Going around topless is one thing, but stalking girls?
Any way you look at it, you are a giant per...
Oh, I are not going to let you say it.
Shut up, you crazy flame spewer!
Bring it on, icy minty fresh!
Please do not fight in front of people's houses!
Lucy, let us go on a job!
So, what kind of job are we going on?
You mean Velveno, the Guild Hunter?
So they found out where he is?
This guy uses some awesome magic!
You can pay your rent with that, Lucy.
Hey, did you hear about what is going on in Acalypha?
Some trade guild is being held up by a group of armed robbers.
And that armed group is actually the Dark Guild, Naked Mummy.
Then the army are not going to be able to handle them...
Lately, the number of Dark Guild incidents has increased a lot.
I am going to go work at a trade guild in Acalypha.
It does not matter what happens to him...
Even if he is that man...
The trade guild Love Lucky in the town of Acalypha.
What is happened to the hostages?
We have put up requests for assistance at nearby wizard guilds.
It is dangerous, so stay back!
I might have family in there!
I have got to do something...
Gate of the Maiden, I open thee!
Princess, is it time for punishment?
I have got a favor to ask...
It seems I am able to enter into the building.
But there are a number of wizards inside.
Will we be okay with just ourselves?
I do not have a choice.
I thought a trade guild would have a ton of cash, but this is it?
We should have just gone for a bank instead.
We are not got no time!
Hurry and put the money in the sacks!
If we do not get this money, we are in big trouble!
We do not got no time!
I will not allow you to lay hands on a lady!
She is a wizard from an official guild!
Be good, or you are going to get hurt!
Today's scissors are sharper than ever-ebi.
I will bring them all down, as it were.
I wonder what magic she will use next?
We also wish to give you our thanks.
You are a wizard from Fairy Tail?
I am so shocked such an incredible person came to save us!
Do not tell me...you just came to town?
I do not have any money, so I walked all the way here.
So all that was for nothing?
You wanted to borrow 100,000 for traveling money?
What kind of warped sense of prices do you have?
Because I heard that the guild you were headed to was attacked!
You came here worried for your dad?
Do not get any strange ideas.
It is not like I have forgiven you.
You have traveled quite a long way, indeed.
I have also had a lot of time to think.
I am going to change who I am.
Even without money, I made it here.
I am sure I can do anything.
This guild is the place I met Layla...
When I was thinking about going independent,
that was right when you were in your mother's stomach.
The two of us quit the guild.
But right then, the guild's signboard broke.
That was quite a strange thing.
The two of us decided that if we had a daughter to name her Lucy.
Do not decide your daughter's name on a whim like that.
But I am glad I got to see you.
Not as Lucky Lucy of the Heartfilias...
I was able to see you as Just Lucy, like you wanted to become.
Could it be you handled everything here yourself?
What was with you all of a sudden?
I was really such a fool...
The main headquarters of the Dark Guild Naked Mummy.
An official guild got in our way!
We could not get our hands on anything!
You said the same line twice!
If they are not got it, they are not got it, Gato-niisan.
-niisan is an honorific for one's older brother.
This is not a time to be laughing, Zato-niisan.
We are coming close to the deadline for paying our dues to Oracion Seis.
This is not a time to be laughing, Zato-niisan.
I have always wondered, but how can they both be the older brother?
There are not any Dark Guilds that disobeys Oracion Seis.
I heard you the first time!
Those bastards suddenly upped the money payments they demand.
What in the world are they plannin'?
The sound of the changing of an era...
Natsu, the master was calling for you.
He said he wanted to talk about some important job.
I wonder if there was some big crisis...
It sounds like we are going to team up with some other guilds to go defeat a Dark Guild!
This does not sound like your everyday gig!
Next time: Allied Forces, Gather Up!
I wonder what kind of people will gather up?
What are you talking about, Happy?
